title: a lot of big xbox stuff leaked
description:
Well, somebody at Microsoft messed up and leaked a bunch of stuff. I guess I’m gonna talk about it. Hopefully Xbox doesn’t say anything too silly, right?

I mean, Phil trying to buy Nintendo was pretty not great, and maybe some of the statements about the competition haven’t aged all that well, but let’s go through some of this mess and try and make some sense of it. Or not.
